details: Learn to dance like your favorite hip hop artist. These classes are high impact and hugely popular. You’ll explore movement as you enjoy incredible music, and a workout that can’t be rivaled in any gym. You’ll also gain confidence that can enrich your overall well-being. details: We offer Contemporary & Modern dance classes that combines elements of several dance genres including modern, jazz, lyrical and classical ballet. Our Contemporary dance instructors strive to connect the mind and the body through fluid dance movements.

name: Jazz
address: {194/2, Fakirapool , Modern Diagnostic Centre. Dhaka.. P.C. 1000, Kotwali, Dhaka.}
details: Jazz dance classes are among our most popular classes, and are always taught by experienced professional choreographers. High energy and fun, these classes are a great form of exercise. You’ll learn jumps, turns, combinations and routines, for a great workout that is incredibly fun and rewarding.

name: Ballet
address: {194/2, Fakirapool , Modern Diagnostic Centre. Dhaka.. P.C. 1000, Kotwali, Dhaka.}
details: We offer ballet classes for kids & teens with no previous experience. These classes are a tremendous way to relieve stress, strengthen your back and shoulders, and improve your overall posture. Ballet training helps prevent injury and improve balance, concentration, alignment, posture and more.

name: Acro
address: {194/2, Fakirapool , Modern Diagnostic Centre. Dhaka.. P.C. 1000, Kotwali, Dhaka.}
details: Our Acro classes for combines classical dance technique with precision acrobatic elements. It is defined by its athletic character, its unique choreography, which seamlessly blends dance and acrobatics, and its use of acrobatics in a dance context. You will gain strength, flexibility, coordination and balance.

name: Technique
address: {194/2, Fakirapool , Modern Diagnostic Centre. Dhaka.. P.C. 1000, Kotwali, Dhaka.}
details: Technique is the basis of all fundamentals of dance, from holding your body correctly while performing, to executing skills properly in a routine. Our Technique classes implore that a good & strong technique extends across all areas of dance, regardless of the style of your routine. This class is crucial for all beginners.

details: You now have a shorter list. Again, sleep on it and look at it with fresh eyes the next day. Cross off the names that you don’t like.
